# ============================================================================
# EVE: Valkyrie – Warzone — Preservation Project .gitignore
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This repo tracks ONLY our own clean-room documentation and analysis scripts.
# It must NOT contain any copyrighted game files, nor raw byte-for-byte dumps
# derived from them (string tables, disassembly listings, extracted assets).
# Those live on disk locally but stay out of version control.
# ============================================================================

# --- The entire shipped game tree (genuine copyrighted files) ---------------
WindowsNoEditor/

# --- Raw derived artifacts (dumps generated FROM the copyrighted binary) ----
# Keep these local only. Distilled findings go into docs/ as prose, not bytes.
# Ignore EVERYTHING under analysis/ — only analysis/scripts/ is re-included below.
analysis/*
analysis/raw/
analysis/compatdata/
analysis/**/*.bin
analysis/**/*.dump
analysis/**/*.pcap
analysis/**/*.pcapng

# --- Defensive catch-all for any game binary/asset extensions ---------------
*.exe
*.dll
*.pak
*.mp4
*.pdb
*.vdf
*.uasset
*.umap
*.ubulk
*.uexp

# --- Tooling / OS noise ------------------------------------------------------
re-venv/
.claude/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store
*.swp

# ============================================================================
# Explicitly TRACK our work product (un-ignore after the broad rules above).
# ============================================================================
!.gitignore
!README.md
!docs/
!docs/**
!analysis/scripts/
!analysis/scripts/**
